steps.instruction:
Made by [Claire Saffitz](https://www.bonappetit.com/recipe/overnight-oats)

1. Combine oats, yogurt, flaxseeds (if using), wheat bran (if using), salt, and 1 cups nut milk in a medium bowl, re-sealable plastic quart container, or large measuring cup
    - If serving with a sweet topping, add agave syrup and stir to combine. Cover and chill overnight.
2. If desired, loosen mixture by stirring in a few more tablespoons of nut milk and let come to room temperature. Top as desired.
